{
  "texts": [
    "Hidden Markov models can adapt to this deformation without exerting too much influence.",
    "A framework utilized by HMM was proposed by Zhang et al. [36], fusing trajectories and hand shape features.",
    "The approach was evaluated effectively on the self-building dataset.",
    "Gao et al. [37] proposed a CSLR system employing SOFM-HMM.",
    "In comparison to the existing system, the performance indicated superiority, and the word recognition rate reached 82.9% on the dataset containing 5113 samples."
  ]
}